<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you are a top executive, but not the chief =
executive officer, at a big investment bank, and you are not particularly n=
ear retirement, probably the job that you want more than any other job is t=
o be CEO of your bank. And then your second choice would probably be to be =
CEO of a different bank. Or <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.=
com/click/32361283.264411/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2Fyd=
GljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDItMDcvYmVkLWJhdGgtYmV5b25kLXNvbGQtc29tZS1zdG9jaz9jbXBpZD1C=
