<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The job of a venture capitalist is to=
 evaluate a lot of potential investments, choose the best ones, and make th=
ose.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The job of a venture capitali=
st is to get <em>access</em> to=C2=A0the best investments, and then make th=
em.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The job of a venture capitalis=
t is to invest in companies and then=C2=A0<em>make=C2=A0</em>those companie=
s better, by serving on boards and imparting wisdom and making introduction=
s and helping the companies hire employees and get customers.</li>
</ol>
